  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个命令行加密工具的状态流转图。这个工具从Infra_IngressController接收参数，然后根据输入决定是显示版本信息、显示帮助、生成密钥、加密还是解密。起点是验证参数的状态q0。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "q0",
        "Validate Args"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，q0是Validate Args。那从q0出发，如果用户带了-v或--version参数，应该跳转到显示版本信息的状态对吧？这个状态我标记为q1。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "q0",
        "q1",
        "-v",
        "--version"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，q1是Display Version Info。显示完版本后程序直接退出，所以q1要连到q7 Exit Program。类似的，-h或--help参数走q2 Display Help，也是显示完就退出。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "q1",
        "q2",
        "q7",
        "-h",
        "--help"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把q0到q1、q0到q2的流转画好了，q1和q2都指向q7。接下来加密流程怎么走？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "q0",
        "q1",
        "q2",
        "q7"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "加密流程是：用户用-e flag带明文进来，先到q3 Generate Key生成密钥，然后到q4 Encrypt Plaintext执行加密，加密完成后进入q5 Decrypt with Key——等等，不对，q5应该是解密用的，加密完应该直接退出。让我重新理一下。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "q3",
        "q4",
        "q5",
        "-e",
        "Encrypt Plaintext"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "我注意到您刚才说q5是Decrypt with Key，但加密流程的最后一步如果是q5就矛盾了。按照命名，q4 Encrypt Plaintext之后应该直接到q7退出。那q5是专门给解密流程用的吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "q4",
        "q5",
        "q7",
        "Decrypt with Key"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "你说得对，我搞混了。修正一下：q4加密完成后直接到q7退出。q5 Decrypt with Key是另一条分支——当用户带-d flag和密文密钥时，直接从q0进入q5解密，解密完也到q7。另外如果参数无效，走q6 Display Usage然后退出。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "q4",
        "q5",
        "q6",
        "q7",
        "-d",
        "invalid args"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成。现在图里有：从Infra_IngressController传入args到q0，q0分出五条路径——version到q1、help到q2、-e加密经q3和q4到q7、-d解密直接到q5再到q7、无效参数到q6再到q7。所有终点都是q7 Exit Program。",
